item.title: This Is My Running Bucket List!
item.description: I would like to be able to do the following things before I die: Visit the republic of Morrocco. Attend a music concert. Climb a mountain (I climbed Mt. Longonot in 2017). Watch Rihanna perform. Live in another country (I lived in TZ for a week üòÅ). Read 1000 books (I’m at 62 officially recorded on GoodReads. Aluta Continua!). Start a company. Get a patent. Write an academic paper. Build my own home.
